â””â”€â”€ packages/
    â”œâ”€â”€ app/
    â”‚   â””â”€â”€ AGENTS.md           # App-specific agent rules
    â””â”€â”€ api/
        â””â”€â”€ AGENTS.md           # API-specific agent rules
```

**Workflow**:
```bash
